        <abstract> 
<p>Asks to borrow FK’s specimen of <hi rend="italic">Conia rosea</hi>. Would like to know if FK collected it himself [in S. Africa] or was given it, because CD has a closely allied species from Australia, which surprises him. [See <hi rend="italic">Living Cirripedia</hi> 2: 335.]</p> 
